nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.core.implSAT

Class SAT_solution

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.core.SolutionInterpreter
      • nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.core.implSAT.SAT_solution

  • public class SAT_solution
extends SolutionInterpreter
    The SAT_solution class describes the solution produced by the SAT solver. It stores the original solution and the mapped one. In case of the parameter unsat being true, there are no solutions.

    It also implements general solution interface SolutionInterpreter.
    Author:
    Vedran Kasalica
